    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1933-09-20T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1933-09-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="94"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d94">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Executive Agreement Series No. 54</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister of External Affairs of the Union of South Africa
                            (<persName type="from">Hertzog</persName>) to the American Minister in
                        the Union of South Africa (<persName type="to">Totten</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Pretoria</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-09-20">20 September,
                            1933</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honour to refer to your letter No. 166
                    of the 17th March last regarding the arrangement between the Union of South
                    Africa and the United States of America providing for navigation by aircraft of
                    each country in the territory of the other and to inform you <pb facs="0232"
                        n="128" xml:id="pg_128"/> that His Majesty’s Government in the Union of
                    South Africa are in accord with the terms of the arrangement which is, word for
                    word as follows:— <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>[Here follows text of the arrangement as given in note No. 166, March 17,
                            printed <hi rend="italic">supra</hi>.]</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>It is further agreed that the arrangement will be operative as from the date of
                    this note.</p>
                <p>I have [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">J. B. M. Hertzog</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
